summary: I did a re-texture of the Mace of Molag-Bal. I made it darker, added blood stains on the teeth, and eyes. Please download, this is my first public re-texture and I hope people will provide constructive criticism and like it.
descriptionHtml:
I did a re-texture of the Mace of Molag-Bal. I made it darker, added blood stains on the teeth, and eyes. Please download, this is my first public re-texture and I hope people will provide constructive criticism and like it. 
[Manual Install]
Download the file.
Extract the file onto your desktop.
Go into your Skyrim directory.
Go in to your Data folder.
Then create or go into your weapons folder.
Place the file into the weapons folder. 
ENJOY THE MOD! 
[Conflicts]
I don\'t know any at the moment.
author: DoctorGleich
